        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4238",
        "content": "One has heard so many dreadful stories of Indian fights and massacres that I tremble a little at the prospect; but I do not mention this to john, for as other women are, like yourself, brave enough to support these dangers, I would not appear a coward in his eyes.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
