        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4238",
        "content": "I hoped that nothing would come of it, but I might have known better.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4238_12895_000025_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4238/12895/4238_12895_000025_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4238",
        "content": "I stopped at Burns' and Hooper's. Burns said he should clear out at once, but Hooper talked about seeing it through.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4238_12895_000029_000013",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4238/12895/4238_12895_000029_000013.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4238",
        "content": "If they succeed there and get lots of booty and plenty of scalps, they may march back without touching you; they will be in a hurry to get to their villages and have their feasts and dancing.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4238_12895_000029_000014",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4238/12895/4238_12895_000029_000014.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4238",
        "content": "If they are beaten off at the settlements I reckon they will pay you a visit for sure; they won't go back without scalps.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4238_12895_000035_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4238/12895/4238_12895_000035_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4238",
        "content": "Of course you will take your rifles with you and keep a sharp lookout; but they will have heard the bell, if they are in the neighborhood, and will guess that we are on the alert, so they are not likely to attempt a surprise.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
